title: Deploy a Helm Chart
tags: @zettel _method helm k8s
roam-id: face266c-ca8b-4e64-8680-04eeccc9ed5e
type: text/markdown

``` shell
cd /path/to/your_chart
helm upgrade --install your_chart . -f values/pretest.yaml

VERSION=<YOUR_VERSION> ENV=<YOUR_ENV> make
helm diff upgrade bird-web bird-web-4.60.0-ug1778154783.tgz
helm upgrade --reset-values --wait bird-web --timeout 5m0s bird-web-4.60.0-ug1778154783.tgz
```

values can be one of the pretest, test, staging, prod etc.
